    "So far, rule-based models are proving indispensable in this regard.",
    "The vital reliability of design tools for structural engineering is evidence of awareness of the risks that AI algorithms hide and the knowledge of how to tackle them without giving up the wide possibilities and fundamental opportunities of applying AI in parametric generative design and solution optimization.",
